## Global Variabel
@BaseUrl = https://pam-2026-p4-ifs23046-be.delcom.org:8080
#@BaseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

## Profile
## ===========================================

### Mengambil semua data profil
# @name GetProfile
GET {{BaseUrl}}/profile
Content-Type: application/json

### Mengambil photo profil
# @name GetProfilePhoto
GET {{BaseUrl}}/profile/photo
Content-Type: application/json


## Plants
## ===========================================

### Mengambil semua data tumbuhan
# @name GetAllPlants
GET {{BaseUrl}}/plants?search=
Content-Type: application/json

### Menambahkan data tumbuhan baru
# @name PostPlants
POST {{BaseUrl}}/plants
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama"

Kangkung
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Brokoli adalah sayuran hijau yang kaya vitamin, mineral, dan serat
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="manfaat"

Membantu detoksifikasi dan menjaga kesehatan mata
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="efekSamping"

Dapat menyebabkan kembung
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="example.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./example.png
--WebAppBoundary--

> {%
    client.global.set("plantId", response.body.data.plantId);
    console.log(client.global.get("plantId"))
%}

### Mengambil data tumbuhan berdasarkan id-nya
# @name GetPlantById
GET {{BaseUrl}}/plants/{{plantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Melihat gambar tumbuhan
# @name GetPlantImageById
GET {{BaseUrl}}/plants/{{plantId}}/image
Content-Type: application/json

### Mengubah hanya data plant berdasarkan id-nya
# @name PutPlantOnlyData
PUT {{BaseUrl}}/plants/{{plantId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama"

Brokoli Update
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Brokoli adalah sayuran hijau yang kaya vitamin, mineral, dan serat
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="manfaat"

Membantu detoksifikasi dan menjaga kesehatan mata
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="efekSamping"

Dapat menyebabkan kembung
--WebAppBoundary--

### Menghapus data plant berdasarkan id-nya
# @name DeletePlant
DELETE {{BaseUrl}}/plants/{{plantId}}
Content-Type: application/json


## Dolls (Versi Boneka)
## ===========================================

### Mengambil semua data boneka
# @name GetAllDolls
GET {{BaseUrl}}/dolls?search=
Content-Type: application/json

### Menambahkan data boneka baru
# @name PostDolls
POST {{BaseUrl}}/dolls
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama"

Labubu The Monsters
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Boneka koleksi populer dari Pop Mart dengan desain monster yang unik dan menggemaskan.
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="merk"

Pop Mart
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="material"

Plush & Vinyl
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="doll_example.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./example.png
--WebAppBoundary--

> {%
    client.global.set("dollId", response.body.data.dollId);
    console.log(client.global.get("dollId"))
%}

### Mengambil data boneka berdasarkan id
# @name GetDollById
GET {{BaseUrl}}/dolls/{{dollId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Melihat gambar boneka
# @name GetDollImageById
GET {{BaseUrl}}/dolls/{{dollId}}/image
Content-Type: application/json

### Mengubah data boneka (tanpa ganti gambar)
# @name PutDollOnlyData
PUT {{BaseUrl}}/dolls/{{dollId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama"

Labubu Update
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Edisi terbatas dengan kostum baru.
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="merk"

Pop Mart
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="material"

Plush / Kain Lembut
--WebAppBoundary--

### Mengubah gambar dan data boneka
# @name PutDoll
PUT {{BaseUrl}}/dolls/{{dollId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama"

Labubu Premium
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Deskripsi terbaru untuk boneka premium.
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="merk"

Pop Mart Special
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="material"

Silicone & Plush
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="new_doll.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./example.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### Menghapus data boneka berdasarkan id
# @name DeleteDoll
DELETE {{BaseUrl}}/dolls/{{dollId}}
Content-Type: application/json